[{"id":"127","parent":"126","text":"• AD: ↓ Aprender nueva info. + déficit en memoria a largo plazo. • Mejora con claves.","guid":"dQxOrjxAucv13iubWrOOOA","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"126","text":"• PD-D: ↓ Memoria libre (relacionada con disfunción ejecutiva)","guid":"9Ci7D1jbOqtxtXFz-wr_Rg","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"126","text":"• DLB: No ↓ inicial, pero progresa → déficit en recuerdo libre, mejora con claves","guid":"ERs52Gb7DTdp7ig2Bwm-3g","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"126","text":"• VaD: ↓ Aprendizaje de nueva info. → problemas de atención","guid":"OxIbVmLytocn6W-QlZJjEQ","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"126","text":"• bvFTD: Amnesia poco presente, afecta memoria de trabajo y episódica","guid":"uGMDKdGpFR65-DpvwxNRcA","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"126","text":"• AD: ↓ Concentración, atención dividida → inicio temprano en algunos casos","guid":"bauq1uM-NFjktqeF2-39VA","children":[]}]},{"id":"133","parent":"125","text":"Atención:","guid":"TXxLq-seynxBJmRzNoyrXg","children":[{"id":"134","parent":"133","text":"• PD-D: ↓ Atención fluctuante > AD","guid":"npe_Kxs_hR4G54iJnEt2bw","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"133","text":"• DLB: Variaciones en atención + ↓ alerta → más prominentes","guid":"Z0n_SD2J62RRrDdwRcgGpA","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"133","text":"• VaD: ↓ Precisión y velocidad en reacción sostenida vs. AD","guid":"CDefYT1UN_6tRQE11AwjOQ","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"133","text":"• bvFTD: Distractibilidad y déficit atencionales prominentes","guid":"2ME3VjfnEKWwXU0-nvUeEw","children":[]}]},{"id":"138","parent":"125","text":"Lenguaje:","guid":"mu9RI6mO32rWtRz8WiDyAA","children":[{"id":"139","parent":"138","text":"• AD: Déficit en denominación, comprensión + memoria semántica","guid":"LFF2EApTdxbi2Duy6HFyHg","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"138","text":"• PD-D: Denominación preservada > lenguaje espontáneo","guid":"5WjXlF3ho93AbpAlwW2Q8w","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"138","text":"• DLB: ↓ Producción espontánea + compresión → asociado a déficit visual","guid":"mcRsH4eIupwWItSv34tJFg","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"138","text":"• VaD: Impacto variable según localización","guid":"tSaVixalzbKnc1DTSKLx1Q","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"138","text":"• bvFTD: Afectación de gramática + conocimiento de palabras.","guid":"xHtlgayTRrJ5NWODnv-EYQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"144","parent":"125","text":"Fx ejecutivas:","guid":"5yT_jehsiHYF4mS3a6iqew","children":[{"id":"145","parent":"144","text":"• AD: Déficit en memoria operativa, abstracción, planeación → impacto en AIVD","guid":"MkRE-_4GlADSONnGEUwV1w","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"144","text":"• PD-D: ↓ Control interno + toma decisiones → más rápido que en DLB","guid":"Ug74rXmecFvsxgvAyPqmrw","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"144","text":"• DLB: ↓ Perseverancia + flexibilidad mental ","guid":"xbjvba-bLQv6iXvLsQV8iA","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"144","text":"• VaD: ↓ Planeación + control → afectación inicial en lóbulos frontales ","guid":"k7tO33EpUcND1SnQ5YIQlQ","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"144","text":"• bvFTD: ↓ Marcado en planeación, perseverancia → desorganización","guid":"hiXx1_mUYwPO0kuLRsvl3g","children":[]}]},{"id":"150","parent":"125","text":"Fx visuoesp.:","guid":"-qd7I-1roJgp-YOXMfzCWw","children":[{"id":"151","parent":"150","text":"• AD: ↓ Percepción visual, juicio espacial → impacto en vida diaria","guid":"ut77Y8AX0bx4jUt2ZXmN6A","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"150","text":"• PD-D: ↓ Rendimiento en pruebas visuoconstructivas","guid":"4u1xMjA5TDrQzm2zMnrhdw","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"150","text":"• DLB: ↓ Percepción, reconocimiento figuras → cuenta rápida","guid":"Q48iOWcNnOW8tzLVX985XA","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"150","text":"• VaD: ↓ Habilidades visuoespaciales en etapas avanzadas","guid":"H6AGfNRZxIqxH35ZQnRPQg","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"150","text":"• bvFTD: ↓ Tareas visuoespaciales avanzadas → menos impacto que AD/DLB","guid":"4n7l2ZI0in9Re2xG5IcHDQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"156","parent":"125","text":"Síntomas\\Nneuropsq.:","guid":"bX87sMkhEfHEXTO7Vx5vrw","children":[{"id":"157","parent":"156","text":"• AD: Cambios personalidad, depresión, ilusiones","guid":"ZH1A21ahKoVGX7PRs1c5aQ","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"156","text":"• PD-D: Apatía, cambios humor, alucinaciones","guid":"EeF6NttBotMQAYPAfo98OQ","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"156","text":"• DLB: Alucinaciones visuales, depresión, delirio","guid":"xVF_nRRWHj8EJVgQiPdXOw","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"156","text":"• VaD: Apatía, irritabilidad, tristeza","guid":"i9GwKOupnLMuhmUD5dutZw","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"156","text":"• bvFTD: Desinhibición, conductas compulsivas","guid":"5m1TIA5tgRF0wl5ExSEuyQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"162","parent":"0","text":"Dx diferencial de demencia","guid":"btZL5xvjVful5knTFC-pEA","children":[{"id":"163","parent":"162","text":"1. Envejecimiento\\Nnormal","guid":"fc2mBXt6mk1VLDnCYFRNOw","children":[{"id":"164","parent":"163","text":"• Inicio insidioso (6ª-7ª década).","guid":"KkIDw3NjGNc5SN77gvJ2CQ","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"163","text":"• Declive leve en memoria episódica y operativa.","guid":"NH-P45One6ZT0mrNX_o2ZA","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"163","text":"• Memoria procedimental y semántica preservadas.","guid":"rc5Z8YLf4ktBRsGmHAHrXQ","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"163","text":"• Independencia funcional.","guid":"5hUqgCksg82PijHVuIQQmg","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"163","text":"• No hay pruebas específicas.","guid":"YiacKESftH7CgzOhGI0VHg","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"163","text":"• Pérdida de volumen cerebral (sust. blanca > sust. gris).","guid":"onaNjBuUHRGSu-ndklk-DQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"170","parent":"162","text":"2. Pseudodemencia\\N(asociada a depresión)","guid":"jrRZoB1ufPa-77_Y74DtMg","children":[{"id":"171","parent":"170","text":"• Relación c/ depresión mayor (↑ adultos mayores).","guid":"nw-D1LzeNI1VBncGMl9P5w","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"170","text":"• Déficit cognitivo tras sx depresivos.","guid":"4gfZJ5Km4jmZzCvq0xGR2A","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"170","text":"• Inicio súbito.","guid":"Iv8eqt5Ibv5yxbfS_ViwgQ","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"170","text":"• Imitación de demencia: quejas de memoria, ánimo ↓.","guid":"Mp1Pktz_WbZKcQVfxDBKPw","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"170","text":"• Mejoría c/ tto antidepresivo efectivo.","guid":"Fg8uhRFKwz06JqyvZi1THg","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"170","text":"• No pruebas específicas.","guid":"MZ27qlHaFT3_8ppckk4w_g","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"170","text":"• Anormalidades estructurales/metabólicas → lesiones límbicas.","guid":"szfFRTe_Y1_NXbuDAHInVg","children":[]}]},{"id":"178","parent":"162","text":"3. Enfermedad de\\NAlzheimer (EA)","guid":"DgveB1t3W6XPqXuR8KF74A","children":[{"id":"179","parent":"178","text":"• Progresión lenta (8-10 años).","guid":"2gNG2ufxNabw4ZegT9e6Pw","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"178","text":"• Déficit episódico memoria → orden:\\Ndenominación → comprensión → fluidez.","guid":"4kisw9-sLH8b3-PeZbRHvg","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"178","text":"• Dx clínico.","guid":"ETx8BURMbWkmZbhrRTtBIQ","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"178","text":"• MRI: Atrofia cortical difusa, hipocampal.","guid":"Z-VR2t-TTwJC1cel7qmhcA","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"178","text":"• LCR: ↓ β-amiloide, ↑ tau fosforilada.","guid":"LzNIgr_uyfIAAVKe5WYuWw","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"178","text":"• Patología: Placas neuríticas (β-amiloide extracelular)\\N+ ovillos neurofibrilares (tau intracelular).","guid":"3d9u9dRPPrkK-Cw_5PCcWg","children":[]}]},{"id":"185","parent":"162","text":"4. Demencia\\Nvascular (DV)","guid":"lf5RYio2ngeXcxH2Lxpsvw","children":[{"id":"186","parent":"185","text":"• Declive cognitivo brusco/ deterioro escalonado.","guid":"FLKwANpOhERyEMIXgRpn4A","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"185","text":"• Déficit focales (e.g., hemiparesia).","guid":"QO91idr4j4ASUaWjnhbh9w","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"185","text":"• CT/MRI: Infartos corticales/lacunares, lesiones sust. blanca.","guid":"Hm_Ur3-SPwSu2-S2tCwzHA","children":[]}]},{"id":"189","parent":"162","text":"5. Demencia c/\\Ncuerpos de Lewy\\N(DLB)","guid":"f8WerLMxGKpCHbYM1_b2Jg","children":[{"id":"190","parent":"189","text":"• Progresión 8-10 años, posible rápida.","guid":"4191l8-r8gftJL-e1S3J8Q","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"189","text":"• Alucinaciones visuales, parkinsonismo.","guid":"TFbsrpk0oJeGwzbU2bER_w","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"189","text":"• Deterioro atención.","guid":"pDMl4AzcUl3TRXElIzZFug","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"189","text":"• MRI: Atrofia cortical leve, sustancia innominada y gris mesopontina.","guid":"NB0C7zUp1oHeNDzuf4O1iA","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"189","text":"• SPECT: ↓ perfusión/metabolismo occipital.","guid":"Xdemg1LQ8PtF4KtonqpSmQ","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"189","text":"• Patología: Cuerpos de Lewy (α-Sinucleína intracelular).","guid":"Zr6qy6-fpGPv9rVQZeaNCA","children":[]}]},{"id":"196","parent":"162","text":"6. Demencia\\Nfrontotemporal\\N(DFT)","guid":"dlArD_A6bjFfCDdr6r9XbQ","children":[{"id":"197","parent":"196","text":"• Inicio 40-69 años.","guid":"Zbkb8_gMS290ekvD_T5oOQ","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"196","text":"• Variante conductual → cambios personalidad, apatía.","guid":"cLtLKn87AO6WEMQlkeYo0w","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"196","text":"• LCR: ↑ Aβ 1-42.","guid":"2VEoXHsWf3g4_tm39n8yMA","children":[]},{"id":"200","parent":"196","text":"• PET/SPECT: ↓ metabólico frontal/temporal.","guid":"AESqUa8dax7kUEGihSlO7A","children":[]},{"id":"201","parent":"196","text":"• MRI: Atrofia frontal/temporal, cortical focal.","guid":"lL9ATQlsB6bGA8nANyeZqg","children":[]}]},{"id":"202","parent":"162","text":"7. Hidrocefalia\\Nnormotensiva (HNT)","guid":"T_M_Xr-Plu9R8sw89kzyTg","children":[{"id":"203","parent":"202","text":"• Reversible potencialmente.","guid":"7vLlVCOfXez3EioO4iMGhA","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"202","text":"• Triada clásica: Marcha alterada, demencia, incontinencia urinaria.","guid":"vq-1AHz-f-EQ_0brLsbreA","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"202","text":"• CT/MRI: Dilatación ventricular c/ hiperintensidades periventriculares.","guid":"Uf79mrAY-ACIFy5HaSR7Kg","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"202","text":"• PL mejora síntomas.","guid":"_6ap3jbRtOTr2647xQr1GA","children":[]}]},{"id":"207","parent":"162","text":"8. Parkinson (DP)","guid":"k3ZqH9yMPOdlcZvOfI2-wQ","children":[{"id":"208","parent":"207","text":"• Deterioro cognitivo en fases avanzadas.","guid":"PTgho8J1txMTvAzGVdu3Vg","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"207","text":"• Sx motores: bradicinesia, temblor reposo, rigidez.","guid":"P4z32BB9uVTC9pLrjHnPfA","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"207","text":"• MRI: Atrofia cortical, hipocampo, amígdala.","guid":"GbM2UwSq2kVuRFxEYXlyQg","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"207","text":"• Degeneración neuronal dopaminérgica (sustancia negra, locus cerúleo).","guid":"tGM5qifiLJLSzBwokm1o2A","children":[]}]},{"id":"212","parent":"162","text":"9. Encefalopatía de Wernicke\\N/ Sx de Korsakoff (EW/SK)","guid":"GsKsofgXXljOYVXVIif_oQ","children":[{"id":"213","parent":"212","text":"• EW (triada): Confusión, ataxia, oftalmoplejía.","guid":"uLj1zBVchtDbiFlWrV806w","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"212","text":"• SK: Amnesia severa (anterógrada y retrógrada).","guid":"-LzSP3CXVKIOQ4GMj-twIA","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"212","text":"• MRI: Atrofia cuerpos mamilares (crónica).","guid":"lnv04_YShINi9BiT1KXkUA","children":[]}]},{"id":"216","parent":"162","text":"10. Neurosífilis tardía","guid":"IeB_yJ5mOWRdNVqkgzkL8w","children":[{"id":"217","parent":"216","text":"• Demencia frontotemporal, psicosis, pupilas Argyll Robertson.","guid":"iGqgOpQH-W9SzNiJFkO-6A","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"216","text":"• Tests treponémicos (FTA-ABS, TPPA): Positivos.","guid":"0nWh5PH9yrBYkiqEUBpXEw","children":[]}]},{"id":"219","parent":"162","text":"11. Enfermedad\\Nde Wilson","guid":"vkAjA-nXn1NZf_NMTa7vZg","children":[{"id":"220","parent":"219","text":"• Hepatopatía → cirrosis y afectación neuropsiquiátrica.","guid":"6Ri5RcOAqkok00YaP2mqDQ","children":[]},{"id":"221","parent":"219","text":"• Anillos Kayser-Fleischer, alteraciones extrapiramidales.","guid":"SzbYNqE7K6ui-BlAbKjJSQ","children":[]},{"id":"222","parent":"219","text":"• MRI: Hiperintensidades putamen, tálamo, tronco encefálico.","guid":"AeB9ZSHioXUVjKDnp-4uWw","children":[]}]},{"id":"223","parent":"162","text":"12. Leucoencefalopatía\\Nmultifocal progresiva (LMP)","guid":"BXnhPyKaS5W_c8IDUWcePQ","children":[{"id":"224","parent":"223","text":"• Inicio insidioso; déficits focales (e.g., hemiparesia, afasia).","guid":"hf2CzIN1csyMrDIq7_s1bA","children":[]},{"id":"225","parent":"223","text":"• MRI: Lesiones sust. blanca multifocales, asimétricas (sin efecto masa).","guid":"1B-Zz_QNEBMd4HKiCeOVkg","children":[]},{"id":"226","parent":"223","text":"• PCR-LCR: Virus JC.","guid":"6zCYWYPacmTAJ5bGYHR25A","children":[]}]},{"id":"227","parent":"162","text":"13. Enfermedad de\\NCreutzfeldt-Jakob (ECJ)","guid":"jsbRx9kzUukeOee9SDrjig","children":[{"id":"228","parent":"227","text":"• Progresión rápida (semanas-meses).","guid":"LPCtk9o4vDEYQU-qW-BPWQ","children":[]},{"id":"229","parent":"227","text":"• Mioclonías desencadenadas x ruidos.","guid":"KmyNb5_zD7fa5J7gUsKXqQ","children":[]},{"id":"230","parent":"227","text":"• LCR: Proteína 14-3-3.","guid":"3pWS6q8BljX4YJ9aFysQ6Q","children":[]},{"id":"231","parent":"227","text":"• EEG: Complejos trifásicos 1-2 Hz.","guid":"2GxcwgORz9QGMY6bjNV6-w","children":[]},{"id":"232","parent":"227","text":"• MRI: Hiperintensidades ganglios basales, corteza frontal.","guid":"NYSP7jDiCVy3sYXcXALwKQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"233","parent":"162","text":"14. Huntington (EH)","guid":"qYXUijfcN9IsjCVFxIWmvA","children":[{"id":"234","parent":"233","text":"• Progresión 15-20 años.","guid":"wxIPmY6CZSipOuLtVEVsfw","children":[]},{"id":"235","parent":"233","text":"• Corea, atetosis, disfunción psiquiátrica.","guid":"0EwXCexeg967jlmffDWkVg","children":[]},{"id":"236","parent":"233","text":"• Genética: Repeticiones CAG.","guid":"85WYOCr9mBrlIuhXtZ0_-Q","children":[]},{"id":"237","parent":"233","text":"• MRI: Atrofia estriatal (núcleo caudado).","guid":"FqjGDbi4jl71_NEQ6CtaMA","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":237,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Neurología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Neurología","filename":"Evaluación neuropsicológica para la detección temprana y el diagnóst-2024","id":"map_1409","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Evaluación neuropsicológica para la detección temprana y el diagnóst-2024"}